'''Sidi Jemour''' ([[Wikipedia:Arabic language|Arabic]]: سيدى جمور) is a [[Wikipedia:marabout|marabout]] located on the west coast of [[Djerba]]. Two scenes from [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''A New Hope'']] were filmed there: a deleted exterior sequence for [[Anchorhead]], and a shot where [[Luke Skywalker|Luke]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi|Obi-Wan]] drive into [[Mos Eisley]].

